        public UriBuilder add(String localname)
        Adds a new part to the URI, after sanitizing it. If localname ends in a "concatenator" character, the character is preserved, but everything else is sent to the sanitizer
        Parameters:

      • namespaceOf

        public boolean namespaceOf(org.openrdf.model.URI uri)
        Checks if the given URI's namespace is the same as our current content. This is a stricter check than contains(org.openrdf.model.Resource) because the namespace must match the this builder's content exactly, and not just start the same way
        Parameters:
        uri - the uri to check
        Returns:
        true, if uri.getNamespace().equals( content.toString() )
